Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:41.57,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Juki a já si sednem za Kjona.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:46.53,Haruhi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jen tak stranou, kam že to bude?
